summary: I AM LISTENING TO AM RADIO. IN NORMAL CITY STREETS. WHEN I GO UNDER A HIGH POWER LINE, THERE IS TREMENDOUS STATIC NOISE AND RADIO VOICE IS COMPLETELY DROWNED OUT. IT IS VERY LOUD. I HAVE OTHER CARS THAT DOES NOT DO THIS ON THE SAME ROAD. I AM CONCERNED ABOUT THIS EMI INTERFERENCE  ON THE REST OF THE ELECTRONIC SYSTEM. DEALER IS NOT AWARE OF ANY RECALL ISSUES AND CANNOT FIX. CALLED HONDA.
